! Word

: speculate [v]:
:: ~= guess 
:: 1. to form an opnion about STH without knowing all the detailes or facts.
:: 2. to buy goods, property, shares, etc., hoping to make a profit when you sell them, but with the risk of losing money.


! Phrase

* why are ....? is it because .....?
** Why do we hace a poor public image? Is it because our product is too expensive?
